          "key": "A",
          "text": "Triangular numbers"
        },
        {
          "key": "B",
          "text": "3\u207f sequence"
        },
        {
          "key": "C",
          "text": "(n+1)3\u207f"
        },
        {
          "key": "D",
          "text": "n\u00b23\u207f"
        }
      ],
      "correctAnswer": "C",
      "explanation": "1/(1-ax)\u00b2 = \u03a3(n+1)a\u207fx\u207f. Here a=3.",
